{"TopicId":219775,"ForumId":208,"TopicTitle":"In the Settings the Auto-hide Navball in Mapview Does the Opposite. On is Off. Off is On","CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-04T10:06:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-04T10:06:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.4.1 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i9 9900K | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A03070ti | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003EIssue:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAuto-hide Navball in Mapview set to On, turns it Off.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAuto-hide Navball in Mapview set to Off, turns it On.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003EVideo Evidence:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/r7evCgU2X1I\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/r7evCgU2X1I\u003C/a\u003E (31 Seconds)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003ECredit for putting Jeb behind Bars in the Video:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/224194-suppise/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022224194\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/224194-suppise/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Suppise\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-10-04T10:15:50Z\u0022 title=\u002210/04/2023 10:15  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Oct 4\u0022\u003EOctober 4, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Anth12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-20T15:03:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe underlying setting says \u0022Show\u0022, but the UI says \u0022Auto-hide\u0022. This could be fixed extremely easily by editing the string in the UI to match the name of the setting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Fx39YYJ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002247.49\u0022 height=\u0022340\u0022 width=\u0022716\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Fx39YYJ.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Y8QJAnv.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002235.50\u0022 height=\u0022407\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Y8QJAnv.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"00Dave","CreatedById":230731,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-07T02:57:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.5 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Win | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ry 7 4800 | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVID RTX 3060 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E16gb\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNav ball and S.A.S. are hidden in map veiw unless selected to be hidden.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthis began around Oct.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also have an Issue with multiple options selected in settings (will be adding link if i can to that Bug)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/20231206214500_1.jpg.f798653c005938508ac1938769b94aae.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ipslightbox=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=KerbalSpaceProgram22023-12-0621-40-45.mp4\u0026amp;fileKey=[!AES128GCM[AvsM4ePATxwTAHo9Lc/DeMmCrGrP/M3JVUAqHXLHhBYyhpT4U6iZdAxmN79vI4s5ZLRNg/JS7qki8YtAqPpcJTDXWOoQKJq%2BDoxS83eaBVjZK57dbeZFbibDYTMTGA==][afb91897e1f1957c29f931ac][8e94f5486d598a962dfdf87d5d32954c]]\u0022\u003EKerbalSpaceProgram22023-12-0621-40-45.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=3XLMK.XIEVES.O.I..json\u0026amp;fileKey=[!AES128GCM[H95WBRMTSDanHGbpbXHNLe90t3Gmspm1YadxVKRjsvrJ82ZEGMkuPuapruujuNr8FEqB3fvGs9xRzJ/34YeW3zHN5So0Kcs=][ab44cbe34ea1d8ff0185ceba][aeb2dd56af8679489e5f4bdf95bae02a]]\u0022\u003E3XLMK.XIEVES.O.I..json\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=3XLMK.XIEVES.O.I..meta\u0026amp;fileKey=[!AES128GCM[lsxEjUBPDQbdsiFCtkGOd6AN%2B8Ews1eVyC8D4hcfqgrKzdsophbaSuVBIBt3S9V7Sq%2BdlT0Dsi06ffeuwEN3AtoLmhAY5rQ=][010ee2727c80a4a13fd1be72][b4448de4450015b90c25f787a8a7c9df]]\u0022\u003E3XLMK.XIEVES.O.I..meta\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-07T08:08:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/230731-00dave/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022230731\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/230731-00dave/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@00Dave\u003C/a\u003E, merged your bug report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anonymous Bug Reporter","CreatedById":231013,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-23T05:57:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 Home 64-bit (10.0, Build 22621) (22621.ni_release.220506-1250) | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-10750H CPU @ 2.60GHz (12 CPUs), ~2.6GHz | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3070 Laptop GPU | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003EMemory: 16384MB RAM Available OS Memory: 16206MB RAM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo navball when in map view. the \u0022yes\u0022 \u0022no\u0022 are both highlighted in settings/ Auto hide navball in map screen. when \u0027yes\u0027 or \u0027no\u0027 are checked the navball does not show when in map view.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022Screenshot2023-12-23165647.png.bfd4ecec24bc88732839fe67c0ad1638.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2023_12/Screenshot2023-12-23165647.png.bfd4ecec24bc88732839fe67c0ad1638.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-23T17:03:28Z\u0022 title=\u002212/23/2023 05:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 23\u0022\u003EDecember 23, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"krbvax","CreatedById":231742,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-31T02:27:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Wine 9.0-rc3 on Linux | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 7 | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA 3060 Ti | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe \u0022Auto-hide Navball in Map View\u0022 user interface setting does not behave as the text suggests: the navball is hidden in map view when the setting is off and displayed when it is on, as if the intended name of the setting is actually \u0022Display Navball in Map View\u0022. (The description shown when hovering over the item, \u0022Show the Navball and its related instruments while in Map view\u0022, also suggests that the setting name was intended to be \u0022Display\u0022 rather than \u0022Auto-hide\u0022).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESeverity:\u003C/strong\u003E Medium\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESteps to reproduce:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen the User Interface category in the settings menu, and set \u0022 Auto-hide Navball in Map View\u0022 to \u0022off\u0022.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLaunch a vehicle.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nEnter map view, and observe whether the navball is displayed.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOpen the settings menu, and change the \u0022 Auto-hide Navball in Map View\u0022 to \u0022on\u0022.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nClose the settings menu, and observe whether the navball is displayed.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EExpected behavior:\u003C/strong\u003E The navball is displayed in step 3 and hidden in step 5.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EObserved behavior:\u003C/strong\u003E The navball is hidden in step 3 and displayed in step 5.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-31T11:34:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231742-krbvax/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022231742\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/231742-krbvax/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@krbvax\u003C/a\u003E, merged your bug report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}